Description-Content-Type: text/markdown; charset=UTF-8; variant=GFM

This package simply wraps Python 3.8 in a wheel, allowing you to install it 
on Red Hat, Centos, Fedora etc that normally only have old versions of Python.
May be able to work around IT protocols that block downloading and installing
software.

Installation and use:

```bash
pip install pyhat

pyhat  # or pyhat myscript.py
```